MOSFET: R_DS(on)=20mΩ, Q_gd=15nC, Q_g=35nC, V_gate=10V, I_gate=1.5A.
(a) I_SW_rms and MOSFET conduction loss
(b) Switching transition time t_sw and switching loss
(c) Gate drive power loss
